flowchart LR
    A[CloudWatch alarm or validated event] --> B[SNS topic]
    B --> C[Lambda validator]
    C --> D{Authorized target?}
    D -- No --> E[Notify responder and stop]
    D -- Yes --> F[Step Functions workflow]
    F --> G[Apply quarantine control]
    G --> H[Preserve evidence]
    H --> I[Notify and record]
